1: type this command: "git clone https://github.com/himynames3r1c/spotigrab"
2: type this command: "ffmpeg -f pulse -i default out.mp3" """dont close"""
3: type pavucontrol: goto recording: change first one to "Monitor of Built-in Audio Analog Stereo"
4: close pavuconrol
5: start spotify
6: start spotigrab.py(Will close first time)
7: unpause current song then just let the songs play and youll get them 

Bugs:
1: turn up volume interrupts the recording

